      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Once it is determined that the incoming materials have met certification standards, and the results have been reviewed and approved, those materials are released to inventory with the appropriate reclassification on the inventory system. Transfer the material from Quality Inspection stock status to unrestricted use stock status. &#10;&#10;&#10;Variants: Batch managed vs. non-batch managed, Split valuation vs. single valuation type Consigned stock vs. owned stock &#10;&#10;"/>
